('Warburtons|Warburtons – Q2 2026','Warburtons','Warburtons – Q2 2026','PS support / Insight review/Vision & Strategy session','UK','In progress',NULL,'Heidi Muhle',1,'Kirsty Thompson - Clarke',42,'N/A',0,NULL,'2026-05-19','2026-06-01','2026-06-01','2026-04-01','Survey 2026-05-19','2026-05-19','4-3 Warburtons Survey goes live I believe from 28th April for 3 weeks so I estimate it would close on or around 19th May. They would like their Results presentation on 26th May. It is quite tight, usually the preview would be 5 working days post survey and the final presentation to senior leadership would be 24-36 hours post that to allow for any updates',NULL,now()),
('Syngenta|Syngenta – Q2 2026','Syngenta','Syngenta – Q2 2026','CS and PS Support','Switserland','In progress',NULL,'Ivan De Las Cuevas Ruiz',55,'Kirsty Thompson - Clarke',39,'Avneeta Solanki',16,'2026-05-05','3rd June to 24th June','w/c 13 July or w/c20 July','2026-07-30','2026-04-01','Delivery end 2026-07-30','2026-07-30','Mail JK: This customer has not confirmed a kick off date but as their next engagement launch is scheduled for June 2026 I anticipate that you should be able to start working with them in April 2026 at the latest (subject to contracts being signed in time!). They have also purchased a ‘bucket of hours’ so they may want to start utilising those hours with you with regular check ins as they are keen on platform optimisation and learning about new features and functionalities. Mail Kirsty: Yarmilla do let me know if I can support in anyway to get this over the line. I am out of the country W/C 29t',NULL,now()),
