('North Mississippi Health Services|','North Mississippi Health Services',NULL,NULL,'US',NULL,NULL,'Heidi Muhle/Angie',73,'Paul Mastrangelo',40,NULL,NULL,NULL,'27-8-2026-13-9-2026',NULL,NULL,'May-2026',NULL,NULL,'Mail Kim to Desiree:Hi Desiree, we can definitely connect whenever you’d like. Aside from the technical bumps we’ve experienced with our firewall blocking your emails to us, we’re in the middle of a Workday implementation and I’ve fallen a bit behind in getting things back to our Legal. That said, our Legal is also swamped and both the MSA and SOW are still with them. Our goal is still to get everything signed off no later than May 1. 1-5-2026 our survey is scheduled to go live on August 27 and close on September 13.',NULL,now()),
