('European Training Foundation (ETF)|ETF-CS-Q4-25-Q1-26|old','European Training Foundation (ETF)','ETF-CS-Q4-25-Q1-26','CS Support','EU','Completed','Medium','Ivan De Las Cuevas Ruiz',61,'N/A',0,'N/A',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-31','2026-01-01','Delivery end 2026-03-31','2026-03-31','Platform Implementation and 1 x survey configuration. Ivan on holiday 9th Jan - 27th Jan in Japan, but customer has been given guidance on what to do while he is away so they can reconvene end of Jan to finalize prep for launch in mid February 13-2-2026 Survey start 16-2 for 3 weeks. Ivan gives a Training for thier leaders on the 23rd of March at 4:30 PM. 2-3 So, we extended the survey by a week. It closes next Monday.. I have to help them release results and have two more calls. I also have a few hours left with them and we discussed having one or more session with them to go over prepping fo',NULL,now()),
